Battera::

Flies up and over to another tree. Sees Ares and fires her optic 
lazars at him. "yeah, no reason to give them an easy target."

She flew infront of CyberShark and yelled. "You coldn't hit the broad 
side of a garage scow." She took off, heading upward into the clouds.

> ::Dachande::
> 
>     He reached up and pulled Battera down. "Hi," He said. "We are 
helping Kit Kat and Destructor."
>     He powered up his shoulder cannon and shot a blast at Ares. 
Then he jumps from his tree to another. "Battera, you might want to 
move."
